XHRM008\", \"type\": \"core\", \"title\": \"Roster staff*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITXHRM009\", \"type\": \"core\", \"title\": \"Lead and manage people*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITXMGT004\", \"type\": \"core\", \"title\": \"Monitor work operations*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITXMGT005\", \"type\": \"core\", \"title\": \"Establish and conduct business relationships\"}, {\"code\": \"SITXWHS007\", \"type\": \"core\", \"title\": \"Implement and monitor work health and safety practices*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITXFSA005\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Use hygienic practices for food safety*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC043\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Work effectively as a cook*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC023\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Use food preparation equipment*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC027\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare dishes using basic methods of cookery*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC028\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare appetisers and salads*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC029\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare stocks, sauces and soups*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC030\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare vegetable, fruit, eggs and farinaceous dishes*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC031\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare vegetarian and vegan dishes*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC035\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare poultry dishes*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC036\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare meat dishes*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC037\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare seafood dishes*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC041\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Produce cakes, pastries and breads*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC042\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare food to meet special dietary requirements*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC026\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Package prepared foodstuffs*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC025\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare and present sandwiches*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC038\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Produce and serve food for buffets*\"}, {\"code\": \"SITHCCC040\", \"type\": \"elective\", \"title\": \"Prepare and serve cheese*\"}]', 'Teaching is conducted in the classroom as well as in the commercial kitchen settings when required to simulate real work environment. The delivery will include face to face teaching, lectures, discussions, research, learning activities, group work, and supervised practical sessions. Students undertaking this course will have access to Student learning resources, learner instructions and guidelines, Commercial Training Kitchen, access to commercial restaurants for their Work Based Training Program.\r\n\r\nAssessments comprise of:\r\nDemonstrations\r\nWritten Questions Answers\r\nCase Studies\r\nProjects', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

